&lt;p&gt;내년에 회사다닐때를 생각하면서 그때까지 천천히 살자.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;여기서의 생활은 연습이라고 생각하자.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>안정</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/hobby/daily/daily54/</link><pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/hobby/daily/daily54/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="안정"&gt;
